<div style="background-color:#fff; width:100%;">
	<img style="margin:0 auto; padding-top:30px; width:80%; display:block;" src="/images/rending/welcome.png" />
	<img style="margin:0 auto; margin-top:20px; width:100%; display:block;" src="/images/rending/illust.png" />
	
	<p style="font-size:36px; font-weight:bold; color:#4b3d3d; margin:4px 0 0 0;">VASKIT</p>
	<p style="font-size:18px; font-weight:bold; color:#ec6e00; margin:26px 0 0 0;">A, B 둘 중에 뭐 사지?</p>
	<p style="font-size:14px; color:#383838; margin:8px 0 0 0; line-height:20px;">
		VASKIT은 사용자들의 참여를 통해<br />
		구매결정고민을 해결하는 서비스입니다.
	</p>
	
	
	<a href="#" onclick="webLoginWithFB(); return false;" style="background:#3b589e; width:200px; height:40px; line-height:40px; display:block; font-size:14px; font-weight:bold; color:#FFFFFF; margin:0 auto; margin-top:30px;-moz-border-radius:20px; -webkit-border-radius:20px; border-radius:20px;">
		<img style="width:10px; margin-bottom:-4px;" src="/images/rending/facebook.png">
		&nbsp;페이스북으로 계속하기
	</a>
	
	<a href="/users/sign_up" style="background:#ee6e01; width:200px; height:40px; line-height:40px; display:block; font-size:14px; font-weight:bold; color:#FFFFFF; margin:0 auto; margin-top:10px;-moz-border-radius:20px; -webkit-border-radius:20px; border-radius:20px;">
		회원가입
	</a>
	
	<a href="/users/sign_in" style="background:#fff; color:#383838; width:200px; border:1px solid #dbdbdb; height:40px; line-height:40px; display:block; font-size:14px; font-weight:bold; margin:0 auto; margin-top:10px;-moz-border-radius:20px; -webkit-border-radius:20px; border-radius:20px;">
		로그인
	</a>
	
	<p style="font-size:12px; color:#9d9ea0; padding:20px 0 40px 0; margin:0;">
		가입 시 <a style="text-decoration:underline;">약관</a> 및 <a style="text-decoration:underline;">개인정보취급정책</a>에 동의하게 됩니다.
	</p>
</div>
<script>
	function webLoginWithFB(){
		$(".loading").show();
		window.location = 'https://www.facebook.com/dialog/oauth?client_id=<%=Facebook::CONFIG["app_id"]%>&redirect_uri=<%=CONFIG["host"]%>/users/facebook&scope=email,public_profile,user_birthday';
	}
</script>

